I keep seeing people say that if you watch this episode then we'll have to wait 2 weeks before s02e03.  Uh, I don't think so...

S02E03 should be up on HBO GO tomorrow and on torrent sites shortly after, following the same pattern as this episode. Hope so.

PS I love getting to watch the episode early, and it's decent quality, but the motion/framerate is a little jerky and detracts slightly from any scenes with a lot of movement. Not complaining, love it, but will re-download in better quality if I watch it again..
